WEBVTT

00:03:57.625 --> 00:04:00.184
to build safety and power for women.

00:04:00.208 --> 00:04:01.684
And through this journey,

00:04:01.708 --> 00:04:03.184
I learned a couple of things,

00:04:03.208 --> 00:04:06.934
and this is what I want to share
with you today, some of these lessons.

00:04:06.958 --> 00:04:08.893
So lesson number one:

00:04:08.917 --> 00:04:10.976
start with what you know.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.643
At the time, I had been doing
Shotokan karate

00:04:13.667 --> 00:04:15.476
for as long as I could remember,

00:04:15.500 --> 00:04:17.476
and so I had a black belt.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:19.892
Yeah. And so, I thought -- surprise.

00:04:19.916 --> 00:04:20.934
(Laughter)

00:04:20.958 --> 00:04:23.684
I thought that maybe
I should go out into my neighborhood

00:04:23.708 --> 00:04:25.601
and teach self-defense to young girls.

00:04:25.625 --> 00:04:27.893
And so I actually went out
and knocked on doors,

00:04:27.917 --> 00:04:30.518
spoke to community leaders,
to parents, to young women,